'''Refugee Facility 17''' was one of the many squalid refugee centers established on [[Ruan]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. It was connected by road to a major [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]], and was built on the site of an old junkyard.

Its [[Species/Legends|species]] included [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]], [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorreans]], [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorians]], [[Gotal/Legends|Gotals]], [[Gand/Legends|Gands]], [[Ruurian/Legends|Ruurians]], [[Bimm/Legends|Bimms]], [[Weequay/Legends|Weequay]], [[Saheelindeeli]], [[Myneyrsh]], [[Vor]]s, [[Rybet/Legends|Rybets]], [[Tammarian]]s, [[Dug/Legends|Dugs]], and 37 [[Ryn/Legends|Ryn]] (including [[Melisma]] and [[Gaph]]). Due to the low standard of living, cramped space, and multitude of species, there was a constant sense of barely-restrained rioting.

It contained [[Noob Hill]] and [[Ryn City]].

